///////////// Demeter - make it green ////////////

Components:
1.Sensors 
2.Camera 
3.Controller (Raspi)
4.LCD display
5.Web-app
6.Arduino script  


Basic functionality of the webservice:
-login prompt
-display of temp, hum, and soil moisture
-livestream of camera 
-time
-adjust max min temp/hum
-adjust light settings 
-manual override of extraction fan, lights, fan
-arlam (parameters exceeded) 
-watering suggestion

LCD display:
-show temp, hum, soil moisture
-watering suggestion

  
